  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DCA Loan Guarantee Agreement</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With GCC-Adaptation funds, USAID/India has provided subsidy amount for this DCA Loan Guarantee Agreement with Rabo India Finance Limited. This agrement is intended to help Rabo India Finance Limited lend to Sustainable Agro-Commercial Finance Limited (SAFL), a relatively young entity with only two full years of operating experience. The loan will allow SAFL to expand its ability to lend to Indian farmers to purchase drip irrigation products that will improve water productivity in agriculture sector. This directly fits within the Adaptation Pillar for improving resilience among small-holder farmers in India.</narrative>
  </description>
